  storyboardPanel: {fileID: 965051024}
  sbImage: {fileID: 134289515}
  sbTitleText: {fileID: 29176928}
  sbBodyText: {fileID: 1394178613}
  sbCounterText: {fileID: 1295573275}
  sbNextButton: {fileID: 1237446813}
  sbPrevButton: {fileID: 1026636334}
  sbContinueButton: {fileID: 147411748}
  storyboardSlides:
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9ce713aaac0af28c489caba6da5774c2, type: 3}
    titleText: Storming the Hub
    bodyText: Breaching the central hub triggers alert mode, swarming advanced AI
      robots with coordinated attacks. Astrid must hack terminals to disrupt the
      core while fending off waves, incorporating FSM-driven behaviors like patrolling-to-chase
      transitions.
  winStoryboardSlides: []
  instructionPanel: {fileID: 1255905585}
  instructionSlides:
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0ba8ec2178bdcf4d380ddf8da838559d, type: 3}
    bodyText: "Eliminate All Threats\n\nThe AI Core is defended by Berserkers, Scout
      Drones, and Heavy units. Berserkers rush aggressively \u2014 use distance and
      cover. Scout Drones fire projectiles from range \u2014 prioritize them. Heavy
      units absorb significant damage \u2014 use your full arsenal."
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a1908afbb8ddabd87bb73fbb096ffcec, type: 3}
    bodyText: 'Find the Deactivation Device


      A Deactivation Device is hidden
      somewhere in the facility. Walk over it to collect it automatically.

      This
      device is required to interact with the terminal switches. You cannot deactivate
      any terminal without it.'
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a86d0d13eb30dda6193e3da4d27e91bf, type: 3}
    bodyText: "Shutdown the AI Core Control\n\nThe AI Core is actively healing all
      enemies every second. Locate and interact with all 4 terminal switches using
      [E]. All 4 terminals must be deactivated to shut down the AI Core. Once offline
      \u2014 enemy auto-healing stops and the Access Key is revealed."
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 24a1acc4690288ecdbd929b1d61368f2, type: 3}
    bodyText: "Find the Access Key\n\nAfter shutting down the AI Core the Access
      Key becomes available. Walk over it to collect it automatically. Head to the
      Exit Door and press [E] to proceed to the Reactor Chamber \u2014 the final
      stage."
  slideImage: {fileID: 855806697}
  slideBodyText: {fileID: 892097}
  slideCounterText: {fileID: 2094508589}
  slideNextButton: {fileID: 953812619}
  slidePrevButton: {fileID: 753573760}
